      "writtenOn": "2026-05-12T13:32:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Fixed in two parts:\n1. Removed the early-return guard from created() — getData always fetches\n   fresh Redfish state on every page entry.\n2. The new clearDevices mutation is called on logout, so stale device state\n   is never carried into a new login session.",
